pandoc 
  to: html
  output-file: series.html
  standalone: true
  toc: true
  number-sections: true
  title-prefix: >-
    Análisis comparativo del desempeño de métodos para el pronóstico de series
    temporales
  section-divs: true
  html-math-method: mathjax
  wrap: none
  default-image-extension: png
  number-offset:
    - 6
  
metadata
  crossref:
    chapters: true
    lol-title: List of list
  document-css: false
  link-citations: true
  date-format: long
  lang: es
  comments:
    hypothesis: true
  bibliography:
    - references.bib
  editor: visual
  theme:
    dark: darkly
    light: cerulean
  grid:
    sidebar-width: 300px
    body-width: 900px
    margin-width: 300px
    gutter-width: 1.5rem
  code-copy: true
  hide-description: true
  title: "[6]{.chapter-number}\_ [Series de Tiempo]{.chapter-title}"
WARNING: Repository links require that you specify a repo-url
